assets.description:
#TiltBrushPaintOff 
#VRArtLive 

The requirements for this piece were to create a monochromatic piece with black, white and one color that was provided to me. I was given pink / fuschia color.  I had one hour to design this, upload to poly and post the link to this poly in the Tilt Brush PaInt Off Discord.

It was alot of fun to compete with all the epic Tilt Brush artists.
